	('Badge of Valor', 'Badge of Valor', 'Champion\'s melee damage for the next 20 seconds will be INCREASED by the targets armor-based ABS instead of decreased.', 3056, 'DOL.GS.RealmAbilities.BadgeOfValorAbilityHandler', '80', 17, NULL, '2000-01-01 00:00:00'),
	('Barrier of Fortitude', 'Barrier of Fortitude', 'Grants the group a melee absorption bonus based on the percentage listed. 30 second duration. (Does not stack with Soldier\'s Barricade or Bedazzling Aura.)', 3015, 'DOL.GS.RealmAbilities.BarrierOfFortitudeAbility', '40', 18, NULL, '2000-01-01 00:00:00'),
	('Bedazzling Aura', 'Bedazzling Aura', 'Grants the group increased resistance to magical damage for 30 seconds by the percentage listed. (Does not stack with Soldier\'s Barricade or Barrier of Fortitude)', 3029, 'DOL.GS.RealmAbilities.BedazzlingAuraAbility', '53', 19, NULL, '2000-01-01 00:00:00'),
	('Berserk', 'Berserk', 'This ability transforms the berserker into a vicious Vendo beast.  While in this form, each hit has a 100% chance to do critical damage, though this is done at the expense of any defensive abilities.', 479, NULL, 'cbd8bab0-35b4-4937-9cd1-3b26534d59c3', 20, NULL, '2000-01-01 00:00:00'),
	('Blade Barrier', 'Blade Barrier', 'For 30 seconds the blademaster parries 90% of all melee attacks. The blademaster is unable to attack during this time. If the blademaster attempts a style while this effect is still up, it will cancel the effect.', 3054, 'DOL.GS.RealmAbilities.BladeBarrierAbility', '78', 21, NULL, '2000-01-01 00:00:00'),
	('Blinding Dust', 'Blinding Dust', 'Insta-cast PBAE Attack that causes the enemy to have a 25% chance to fumble melee/bow attacks for the next 15 seconds.', 3039, 'DOL.GS.RealmAbilities.BlindingDustAbility', '63', 22, NULL, '2000-01-01 00:00:00'),
	('Blissful Ignorance', 'Blissful Ignorance', 'Allows the Savage to fire all savagery buffs for a single round without paying any hit point penalty.', 3068, 'DOL.GS.RealmAbilities.BlissfulIgnoranceAbility', '92', 23, NULL, '2000-01-01 00:00:00'),
	('Bodyguard', 'Bodyguard', 'Ability that protects a groupmate from enemy melee attack. Target of Bodyguard can\'t be attacked by melee until the bodyguard is killed or moves out of range. Target of Bodyguard must not be moving.', 2648, NULL, 'Bodyguard', 24, NULL, '2000-01-01 00:00:00'),
	('Boiling Cauldron', 'Boiling Cauldron', 'Summons a large cauldron that boils in place for 5 seconds before spilling and doing damage to all those nearby.', 3085, 'DOL.GS.RealmAbilities.BoilingCauldronAbility', 'BoilingCauldron', 25, NULL, '2000-01-01 00:00:00'),
	('Bolstering Roar', 'Bolstering Roar', 'A Point-Blank Area Effect attack with a 250 radius that breaks root, breakable snares and mesmerization effects on group members. If the tank is CC\'d (other than root) they will have to purge themselves or wait for CC to wear off, then fire this. Re-usable every 10 minutes. ', 974, NULL, 'tank_ability_bolsteringroar', 26, NULL, '2000-01-01 00:00:00'),
	('Call of Darkness', 'Call of Darkness', 'When active, the necromancer can summon a pet with only a 3 second cast time. The effect remains active for 15 minutes, or until a pet is summoned. ', 3050, 'DOL.GS.RealmAbilities.CallOfDarknessAbility', '74', 27, NULL, '2000-01-01 00:00:00'),
	('Calming Notes', 'Calming Notes', 'Insta-cast spell that mesmerizes all enemy pets within 750 radius for 30 seconds.', 3044, 'DOL.GS.RealmAbilities.CalmingNotesAbility', '68', 28, NULL, '2000-01-01 00:00:00'),
