	('Chain Lightning', 'Chain Lightning', 'Casts a lightning bolt at the enemy target and hits up to 5 targets (player or pet). If there is only one target available, the spell will hit once. If there are multiple targets, the spell has a chance to jump from target to target and back to the prior target. With each jump, the damage of the spell is reduced by 25%.', 3066, 'DOL.GS.RealmAbilities.ChainLightningAbility', '90', 33, NULL, '2000-01-01 00:00:00'),
