	('Critical Shot', 'Critical Shot %n Ability', 'Must be fired from stealth, very high damage, average range and average draw time.<br><br>Target get 10sec 50% resistance against critical or power shots.<br><br>Will bypass Bladeturn, but not break it; as well as bypassing Brittle Guards, Intercept, Guard and Block.', 413, NULL, '12c8a5f9-5509-46c3-b61b-7a0cafd8b91e', 40, NULL, '2000-01-01 00:00:00'),
