	('Dashing Defense', 'Dashing Defense', 'The tank can block and parry for all groupmates within a 1000 radius for the duration listed. Each attack only has the chance of being blocked/parried once, regardless of how many characters in a group have Dashing Defense active at one time.', 3032, 'DOL.GS.RealmAbilities.DashingDefenseAbility', '56', 42, NULL, '2000-01-01 00:00:00'),
