	('Initiate of the Hunt', 'Initiate of the Hunt', 'This ability is Native to the Hero. He can shapeshift into a fearsome stag-headed Hunstman of Celtic Lore, once per 20 minutes, lasting 30 seconds. This level of Spirit of the Hunt grants a 20% hitpoint bonus.', 0, NULL, 'f1888ac8-9f9c-41d7-8b9d-b8e8aa62f389', 74, NULL, '2000-01-01 00:00:00'),
