	('Mark of Prey', 'Mark of Prey', 'Grants all members of the Vampiir\'s group a 30 second damage add that stacks with all other forms of damage add. All damage done via the damage add will be returned to the Vampiir as power.', 3089, 'DOL.GS.RealmAbilities.MarkOfPreyAbility', 'b426246-v246236b2', 82, NULL, '2000-01-01 00:00:00'),
